c: 24
v: 11
t: "Pellet, Й“en adduЙ“e penaale Й—en ko Й“e jamaa jeyaaЙ—o e mooЙ—on, wata on sikku Й—um ko bone mo'on; ko woni Й—um ko moЖґЖґere mo'on. No woodani kala neЙ—Й—o immorde e maЙ“Й“e ko o faggitii kon e junuubu, on fawtiiЙ—o mawЙ—um [junuubu on] immorde e maЙ“Й“e, no woodani mo Lepte mawЙ—e"